			subtitle: "Craft Quartz Enriched Iron \u2014 used in every Refined Storage component."
			x: 2.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["D011"]
			description: [
				"§eBasic Processors§r are the entry-tier processor used in most starter RS blocks."
				""
				"§7Two-step process:§r"
				"1. Craft a §7Raw Basic Processor§r from Quartz Enriched Iron + Redstone + Silicon"
				"2. §7Smelt§r the raw processor in a furnace \u2014 this produces the finished §eBasic Processor§r"
				""
				"Make at least 4. You'll need them for the Machine Casing, Controller, Disk Drive, and Grid."
			]
			icon: "refinedstorage:basic_processor"
			id: "D012"
			rewards: [
