		{
			dependencies: ["D024"]
			description: [
				"The §eWithering Processor§r is the high-end processor required for all Extra Disks. Like base RS processors it's a two-step process \u2014 craft a §7Raw Withering Processor§r first, then §7smelt it§r in a furnace."
